	k_wales={
		capital="c_cardiganshire"
		color={ 135 25 3 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		landless=no
		definite_form=no
		ruler_uses_title_name=no
		ai_primary_priority={
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture = culture:welsh
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					OR = {
						culture = culture:cumbrian
						culture = culture:cornish
						culture = culture:breton
					}
				}
				add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
			}
		}
		can_create={
			trigger_if = {
				limit = {
					is_ai = yes
				}
				culture = { has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic }
			}
		}
	}

e_germany={
	capital="c_nassau"
	color={ 190 200 190 }
	color2={ 220 220 20 }
	k_saxony={
		capital="c_dessau"
		color={ 120 25 25 }
		landless=no
		definite_form=no
		ruler_uses_title_name=no
		ai_primary_priority={
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture = { has_cultural_pillar = heritage_central_germanic }
				}
				add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
			}
		}
		can_create={
			trigger_if = {
				limit = {
					is_ai = yes
				}

			if = {
				limit = {
					culture = culture:latgalian
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					NOT = {
						culture = culture:latgalian
					}
				}
				add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
			}
		}
	}

	ruler_uses_title_name=no

		if = {
			limit = {
				culture = { has_cultural_pillar = heritage_baltic }
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
		else_if = {
			limit = {
				culture = { has_cultural_pillar = heritage_balto_finnic }
			}
			add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
		}
	}

	capital="c_ile_de_france"
	color={ 11 22 170 }
	color2={ 255 255 20 }
	k_france={
		capital="c_ile_de_france"
		color={ 15 27 187 }
		color2={ 255 255 20 }
		landless=no
		definite_form=no
		ruler_uses_title_name=no
		ai_primary_priority={
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture = culture:french
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					OR = {
						culture = culture:norman
						culture = culture:occitan
					}
				}
				add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
			}
		}
	}
	landless=no
	definite_form=no
	ruler_uses_title_name=no
	ai_primary_priority={
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture = culture:french
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
		if = {
			limit = {
				OR = {
					culture = culture:norman
					culture = culture:occitan
				}
			}
			add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority={
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture = culture:occitan
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					OR = {
						culture = culture:norman
						culture = culture:french
					}
				}
				add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
			}
		}
	can_create={
			trigger_if = {
				limit = {
					is_ai = yes
				}
				NOT = { has_title = title:k_france }
			}
		}
